程序包的使用
org.diku.dms.bds_project.query

  • 使用org.diku.dms.bds_project.query的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.diku.dms.bds_project  
    org.diku.dms.bds_project.query  
  • org.diku.dms.bds_project使用的org.diku.dms.bds_project.query中的类 
    类 说明
    EdgePattern
    An edge pattern consists of source vertex, destination vertex and edge attribute.
    Match
    `Match` is the data type stored in MatchesRDD to represent a match of an edge pattern, a partial pattern or even the entire pattern graph.
    MatchesRDD
    A MatchesRDD instance stores a collection of matches to a partial pattern as an RDD.
    PatternGraph
    `PatternGraph` represents a pattern graph, which consists a set of query edges and a set of query vertices.
  • org.diku.dms.bds_project.query使用的org.diku.dms.bds_project.query中的类 
    类 说明
    EdgePattern
    An edge pattern consists of source vertex, destination vertex and edge attribute.
    Match
    `Match` is the data type stored in MatchesRDD to represent a match of an edge pattern, a partial pattern or even the entire pattern graph.
    MatchesRDD
    A MatchesRDD instance stores a collection of matches to a partial pattern as an RDD.
    MatchMeta
    `MatchMeta` contains some necessary information regarding the partial pattern that the data of MatchesRDD matches to.
    QueryVertex
    A query vertex consists of a vertex id and a predicate on vertex for match.
    VertexPredicate
    `type` refers to whether this query vertex should match a data vertex id or a vertex attribute.
